    "description": "Read a plist file. fp should be a readable and binary file object. Return the unpacked root object (which usually is a dictionary). The fmt is the format of the file and the following values are valid: None: Autodetect the file format FMT_XML: XML file format FMT_BINARY: Binary plist format The dict_type is the type used for dictionaries that are read from the plist file. When aware_datetime is true, fields with type datetime.datetime will be created as aware object, with tzinfo as datetime.U...",
